user_prompt: The moment I ride the tube down from the high water slide of a fancy water park. The gaze follows the endless curves and rotating structures of the slide, vividly hitting the face with spray. The tube slides off at a high speed, and my heart throbs whenever I pass thrilling curves along the wall of the slide. A clear sky and a bright sun shine around me, and virtual water droplets bounce around the tube. Finally, at the end of the slide, it lands quickly into the water, and the feeling of being buried in the cool water winds throughout my body."
prompt_variant: The riders experience an exhilarating descent as they zoom down the high water slide, water spraying around them.
